                                        <head>
                                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                                        </head>
                                        <p>The information set forth above is derived from the
                                            memorandum of conversation printed <hi rend="italic">infra</hi> and from the detailed accounts of the
                                            conversation in <persName corresp="#p_ACHESONDG1">Acheson</persName>, <hi rend="italic">Sketches from
                                                Life</hi>, pages 113 ff. and <persName corresp="#p_ACHESONDG1">Acheson</persName>, Present
                                            at the Creation, pages 627–628. No other official record
                                            of this conversation, other than the memorandum printed
                                            here, has been found.</p>
